about.summary: A backport of recent additions to the `collections.abc` module.

name: backports_abc
raw_recipe:
{% set version="0.4" %}

package:
  name: backports_abc
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: backports_abc-0.4.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/b/backports_abc/backports_abc-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: 0b65a216ce9dc9c1a7e20a729dd7c05b

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - backports_abc

about:
  home: https://github.com/cython/backports_abc
  license: PSF 2
  summary: A backport of recent additions to the `collections.abc` module.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
